Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.mealplanit.model.Person

  • public class Person
extends Object
    Model for creating the Person table in the database that allows accessors and mutators to access or change the the information in the table. This model holds the information for all the users in the database.
